query:
INSERT INTO reschedule_history (userId, waypointId, routeId, routeName, contactName, address, rescheduledDate, status)
SELECT 
  r.userId,
  rw.id,
  r.id,
  r.name,
  COALESCE(rw.contactName, 'Unknown'),
  COALESCE(rw.address, 'No address'),
  rw.rescheduledDate,
  'pending'
FROM route_waypoints rw
JOIN routes r ON rw.routeId = r.id
WHERE rw.rescheduledDate IS NOT NULL;
